sition:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/eab77/Unknown.jpg 92w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/88c55/Unknown.jpg 184w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/f4ac5/Unknown.jpg 368w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/8033b/Unknown.jpg 552w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/d23b4/Unknown.jpg 654w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 100vw, 368px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 100vw, 368px\" srcSet=\"/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/eab77/Unknown.jpg 92w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/88c55/Unknown.jpg 184w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/f4ac5/Unknown.jpg 368w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/8033b/Unknown.jpg 552w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/d23b4/Unknown.jpg 654w\" src=\"/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/f4ac5/Unknown.jpg\" alt=\"Home Vestors Logo\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/eab77/Unknown.jpg 92w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/88c55/Unknown.jpg 184w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/f4ac5/Unknown.jpg 368w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/8033b/Unknown.jpg 552w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/d23b4/Unknown.jpg 654w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 100vw, 368px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 100vw, 368px\" srcset=\"/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/eab77/Unknown.jpg 92w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/88c55/Unknown.jpg 184w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/f4ac5/Unknown.jpg 368w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/8033b/Unknown.jpg 552w,\n/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/d23b4/Unknown.jpg 654w\" src=\"/static/01ae94fdcf0d92552304dbc39af4e7ab/f4ac5/Unknown.jpg\" alt=\"Home Vestors Logo\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>The PM Group is excited to announce our new client, HomeVestors, also known as the We Buy Ugly Houses people. They are the number one home buyer in America and buy houses every day for cash. HomeVestors will close on your house in as quickly as 30 days when you need to move for a number of reasons including structural or cosmetic issues, foreclosure, job relocation, or you’re just tired of your ugly home! Make sure to keep an eye out for their commercials on TV and their billboards throughout the city. The PM Group is honored to be selected to represent the HomeVestors’ San Antonio franchise group in marketing their business.</p>\n<p><b>About The PM Group:</b> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 29 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <i>San Antonio Business Journal</i>. The PM Group’s client roster spans various industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date raised over $1 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations.</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Closes on #1 Home Buyer in America","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Closes on #1 Home Buyer in America","url":"/the-pm-group-closes-on-1-home-buyer-in-america/"}],"title":"PMG Closes on #1 Home Buyer in America | The PM Group","metaDesc":"The PM Group is proud to announce our new client, HomeVestors, also known as the We Buy Ugly Houses people, who are the number one home buyer in America.","focuskw":"homevestors","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"PMG Closes on #1 Home Buyer in America | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"The PM Group is proud t